{"id": "1395101523599687710", "channel_id": "1394569081830506567", "author_id": "605159327942049844", "author_name": "ev_6185", "content": "**My Translation:**\n\n“To feed, is the first thing we ever learn. Come closer, dear guest. \nBe not afraid, feel my teeth and tongue graze across your skin and viscera.“ \n\n“Ah… my delicacy… my beloved…” \n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n**Game Translation:** \n\n\"To dine is the first art we ever learn. Come, dearest guest, come closer to me.\nFear not. Relish the caress of my lips, my teeth, as they worship your skin and viscera.\"\n\n\"Ah… my exquisite morsel… my delicious beloved…\"", "timestamp": "2025-07-16T17:55:22.959000+00:00", "thread_id": "1394569081830506567"}
