{"id": "1394979286447947798", "channel_id": "1394979286447947798", "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "content": "管风琴弹奏腐朽，高脚杯中血液正黏稠；\n群尸从坟墓爬出，跳着诡异的踢踏舞步。\n\n墓园舞会，不过是对礼节的戏仿；\n尖利爪牙，袒露着最原始的欲望；\n在餐盘中下入致死量的贪婪，再将那口鲜活吞下；\n逝者的记忆、亡魂的密语，滑入胃袋溶进血肉……\n终于！葬骸城在进食中获得了安宁与永恒。\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nThe pipe organ plays a dirge of decay, blood thickens in goblets. \nCorpses claw free from graves, dancing a grotesque tap. \n\nThe graveyard ball is but a mockery of etiquette; fangs and talons bare primal desire.\nLace the plate with lethal greed, then swallow the morsel of life whole—memories of the dead, whispers of ghosts, slip into the stomach, dissolving into flesh…\nAt last! The city of Necrovia finds peace and eternity in its feast.", "timestamp": "2025-07-16T09:49:39.351000+00:00", "thread_id": "1394979286447947798", "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 11}, {"emoji": "dishes", "emoji_id": "1356083313063759922", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "love", "emoji_id": "1356053099931897977", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "🇱", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🇪", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🇬", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🇸", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1394979287836393523", "filename": "2-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 7953366, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1394979286447947798/1394979287836393523/2-.jpg?ex=69ccea33&is=69cb98b3&hm=6ad41ffc7149ebebe38f17cf4796573b88a2fa5fc89367d4ad0c5c5b61cba641&"}]}
